        <updateDate>2020-06-17T18:46:12Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Service Assurance Act of 2020</b></p> <p>This bill exempts nonprofit organizations from liability for any act or omission relating to harm arising from exposure to, or infection by, the coronavirus (i.e., the virus that causes COVID-19) during the COVID-19 public health emergency. However, this&nbsp;exemption does not apply with respect to&nbsp;acts or omissions that constitute willful or criminal misconduct, gross negligence, reckless misconduct, or conscious and flagrant indifference to the rights or safety of the individual harmed. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
